# Surrogate disciplines

A [SurrogateDiscipline][gemseo.disciplines.surrogate.SurrogateDiscipline] is built
from the name of an [BaseRegressor][gemseo.mlearning.regression.algos.base_regressor.BaseRegressor] and its options.
These names and options are listed below.

!!! warning

    Some algorithms can require the [installation][installation] of GEMSEO with [dependencies][dependencies]
    and others can depend on [plugins][plugins].

!!! note

    All the features of the wrapped algorithm libraries may not be exposed through GEMSEO.

